身体还是清楚的知道你在没事儿饿着它玩，于是来一记致命反击让你胖！这还不够说明问题嘛…… 为什么一节食就暴食，为什么不管吃多少蔬菜，喝多少水把自己“撑”个半死，你还是觉得饿，还是想吃，还是会义无反顾的暴食？因为你的身体和大脑，在面对吃这件事情上，比你聪明的可太多了！所以想要瘦，想要长久有效不反弹的瘦，还是别没事儿自己作着节食了。要知道：一朝节食，注定暴食！参考文献：①Sumithran, P., Prendergast, L. A., Delbridge, E., Purcell, K., Shulkes, A., Kriketos, A., & Proietto, J. (2011). Long-term persistence of hormonal adaptations to weight loss. New England Journal of Medicine, 365(17), 1597-1604.②Sumithran, P., & Proietto, J. (2013). The defence of body weight: a physiological basis for weight regain after weight loss. Clinical Science,124(4), 231-41.③O'Connor, K. L., Scisco, J. L., Smith, T. J., Young, A. J., Montain, S. J., & Price, L. L., et al. (2016). Altered appetite-mediating hormone concentrations precede compensatory overeating after severe, short-term energy deprivation in healthy adults. Journal of Nutrition. 《一平米健身》，多谢支持！查看知乎原文
